<HTML>
#set $Response.ContentType = "text/html"
<BODY>
<EM>This example demonstrates usage of </EM><TT>CompositeTypeHandler</TT><EM>:
values from multiple input fields can be composed to a value of a single
Java type:
<P>

   <FORM METHOD="POST">
   <INPUT TYPE="HIDDEN" NAME="date" VALUE="day,month,year">

   <TABLE>
      <TR><TD>
         Day (1-31):</TD><TD><INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="day">
      </TD></TR>
      <TR><TD>
      Month (1-12):</TD><TD><INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="month">
      </TD></TR>
      <TR><TD>
      Year (ex.: 2001):</TD><TD><INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="year">
      </TD></TR>
   </TABLE>

   <INPUT TYPE="Submit" NAME="action" VALUE=" Submit ">

   </FORM>
</BODY>
</HTML>
